	 <h1 id="getting-started">Getting Started</h1>
   <hr />
</div>
You can open spectra from your email, file, other applications, by selecting the "Copy To InterSpec" option.  
You can also open files from within InterSpec by going to the menu then <em>Spectra</em>&rarr;<em>Open File...</em>, and then browsing for files.

InterSpec can open nearly all common gamma spectra formats, including N42, SPE, PCF, SPC, CSV, and other detector specific formats.


